17.5 Reporting claims
:SKRSLUT.
.br
On returning home, a claim report is to be submitted to
Privatsikring. In order to ensure correct processing of the case, all
relevant documents must be enclosed, including information
about any corresponding insurance policies taken out with a
different company. The insured is obliged to present documentation
such as unused airline tickets, receipts and itineraries (all as
original documents).
.sp 5mm
.of 5mm
*¤traffic accident or mechanical breakdown where assistance has been
provided by an assistance company.
.of
