17.3 Coverage - Rejoining the route in the event of delays to a connecting
flight.
:SKRSLUT.
.br
The insurance covers expenses up to DKK 10,000 per person for new
airline tickets (max. economy class) and DKK 1,000 per person per day
for hotel accommodation and meals on account of late arrival for a
reserved connecting flight.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
17.3.1 Acceptable reasons for the insured failing to arrive on time for
his/her connecting flight are:
.of 5mm
*¤the insured, through no fault of his/her own, failing to arrive on
time for the connecting flight and there being no alternative flight
available
.of
.of 5mm
*¤unexpected weather conditions, natural disasters or technical grounds.
.of
